<h2>Rave Flyer Archive</h2>
<p>Before social media, the photocopied flyer was the only advertising. Handed outside tube stations, left in record shops. Procedurally generated in the spirit of the originals.</p></div>
<div class="ctrl-row hidden stagger-2">
<button class="btn btn-accent" id="regenFlyers">Generate New Archive</button>
<span style="font-size:0.65rem;color:var(--dim);">12 flyers · hover to lift · click to expand</span>
</div>
<div class="flyer-grid hidden stagger-3" id="flyerGrid"></div>
<div class="modal-overlay" id="flyerModal">
<div class="modal-box">
<button class="modal-close" id="flyerModalClose">✕</button>
