</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- ═══════════════════════════════ SECTION 7 — CROWD SIMULATOR ════════════ -->
<section id="crowd">
<div class="hidden stagger-1"><div class="section-label">Boids Simulation</div>
<h2>Crowd Energy Simulator</h2>
<p>Top-down warehouse floor. Each dot follows Boids rules — separation, alignment, cohesion. Drop the bass and watch them surge.</p></div>
<div class="two-col" style="align-items:start;">
<div class="hidden stagger-2">
<div class="canvas-wrap"><canvas id="crowdCanvas" style="height:420px;"></canvas></div>
<div class="energy-bar-wrap" style="margin-top:0.5rem;"><div class="energy-bar-fill" id="energyBar"></div></div>
<div id="energyLabel" style="font-size:0.6rem;color:var(--dim);margin-top:0.3rem;text-align:center;">Energy: 50%</div>
</div>
<div class="hidden stagger-3">
<div class="card">
<div class="section-label">Controls</div>
<div class="ctrl-row">
<button class="btn drop-btn" id="preDropBtn" style="font-size:0.65rem;">PRE-DROP</button>
<button class="btn drop-btn btn-accent" id="dropBtn" style="font-size:0.65rem;">DROP</button>
<button class="btn drop-btn btn-amber" id="breakdownBtn" style="font-size:0.65rem;">BREAKDOWN</button>
</div>
<div class="slider-row" style="margin-top:0.75rem;">
<span class="slider-label">BPM</span>
<input id="crowdBpm" max="180" min="100" step="1" type="range" value="160"/>
<span class="slider-val" id="crowdBpmVal">160</span>
</div>
<div class="slider-row">
<span class="slider-label">Density</span>
<input class="amber" id="crowdDensity" max="200" min="30" step="1" type="range" value="80"/>
<span class="slider-val amber" id="crowdDensityVal">80</span>
</div>
<div class="slider-row">
<span class="slider-label">Cohesion</span>
<input id="crowdCohesion" max="100" min="0" step="1" type="range" value="40"/>
<span class="slider-val" id="crowdCohesionVal">40</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class="card" style="margin-top:1rem;">
<div class="section-label">State</div>
<div id="crowdStateDisplay" style="font-size:0.85rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--accent);text-shadow:0 0 8px rgba(57,255,20,0.5);">PRE-DROP</div>
<div style="font-size:0.68rem;color:var(--dim);margin-top:0.4rem;line-height:1.6;">Boids: separation radius 25px · cohesion radius 60px · max speed scales with BPM. Laser sweeps sync with beat phase.</div>
</div>
<div class="card-quote" style="margin-top:1rem;"><p>"On the dancefloor, the individual disappears into the collective. The rave was Britain's closest brush with utopian communism." — Jeremy Gilbert</p></div>
</div>
